      <title>Verisk Maplecroft 称，战火正席卷非洲 10% 的地区</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-21/fighting-is-engulfing-10-of-africa-verisk-maplecroft-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据 Verisk Maplecroft 称，非洲约有 10% 的地区陷入冲突，过去三年来战斗不断蔓延和加剧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-21/fighting-is-engulfing-10-of-africa-verisk-maplecroft-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
