    <item>
      <title>罗马尼亚极端民族主义总统候选人誓言终止对基辅的军事援助</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-21/romanian-ultra-nationalist-presidential-hopeful-vows-to-end-military-aid-to-kyiv</link>
      <description><![CDATA[罗马尼亚极端民族主义政党的领导人表示，如果他当选最高职位，将停止对乌克兰的军事援助。凭借其高人气，他在该国总统大选前的民意调查中位居第二。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-21/romanian-ultra-nationalist-presidential-hopeful-vows-to-end-military-aid-to-kyiv</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普威胁迫在眉睫，中国总理李克强将与外国企业首席执行官会面</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-21/chinese-premier-li-to-meet-foreign-ceos-as-trump-threat-looms</link>
      <description><![CDATA[正当企业准备应对唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 提高中国产品关税的威胁时，中国国务院总理李强预计将于周一在北京举行的供应链博览会前会见外国企业高管。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-21/chinese-premier-li-to-meet-foreign-ceos-as-trump-threat-looms</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 04:32:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国央行调查显示对美国政策变化风险的担忧浮现</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-21/bok-survey-shows-concerns-emerging-on-us-policy-change-risk</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国银行的一项调查显示，总统大选之后，美国政策风险已成为韩国金融家和专家关注的一大担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-21/bok-survey-shows-concerns-emerging-on-us-policy-change-risk</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 03:25:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国称其军队正在南海支援菲律宾</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-21/us-says-its-forces-are-supporting-philippines-in-south-china-sea</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国称其军队支持菲律宾在有争议的南海的军事行动，马尼拉和北京在该海域因主权主张发生冲突。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-21/us-says-its-forces-are-supporting-philippines-in-south-china-sea</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 02:11:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>五角大楼负责人称中国拒绝在其亚洲之行期间举行会晤</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-21/pentagon-chief-says-china-declined-meeting-during-his-asia-visit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国国防部长劳埃德·奥斯汀证实，中国国防部长决定本周不与他在老挝会晤，这让人想起在唐纳德·特朗普准备就任总统之际，世界两大经济体之间的关系依然紧张。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-21/pentagon-chief-says-china-declined-meeting-during-his-asia-visit</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 02:09:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>越南称教皇弗朗西斯希望“很快”访问该国</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-21/vietnam-says-pope-francis-would-like-to-visit-country-soon</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据越南政府网站发表的声明称，梵蒂冈官员表示，在收到越南总理范明政的访问邀请后，教皇方济各希望“很快”访问越南。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-21/vietnam-says-pope-francis-would-like-to-visit-country-soon</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 01:25:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰国保守派掌权后，针对总理的抱怨不断增加</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-21/complaints-against-new-thai-pm-pile-up-as-old-guard-wields-power</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国活动家 Ruangkrai Leekitwattana 每天在卧室里花 10 个小时撰写投诉文章 — — 大部分是针对泰国的新领导人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-21/complaints-against-new-thai-pm-pile-up-as-old-guard-wields-power</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 01:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登政府寻求取消乌克兰 46 亿美元债务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-21/biden-white-house-seeks-to-cancel-4-6-billion-of-ukraine-s-debt</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据彭博新闻社获得的一封信显示，拜登政府告诉国会，计划取消乌克兰所欠的 46.5 亿美元债务，这是当选总统唐纳德·特朗普上任前为加强对基辅的支持而采取的一系列举措中的最新举措。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-21/biden-white-house-seeks-to-cancel-4-6-billion-of-ukraine-s-debt</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 00:38:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马斯克和拉马斯瓦米计划为联邦工作人员实行五天工作周</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-20/trump-picks-former-attorney-general-whitaker-as-nato-ambassador</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃隆·马斯克和维韦克·拉马斯瓦米——当选总统唐纳德·特朗普挑选的领导新成立的政府支出审查工作组的人——表示，他们将推动取消联邦工作人员的在家办公政策，这一想法可能引发新政府和政府雇员工会之间的冲突。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-20/trump-picks-former-attorney-general-whitaker-as-nato-ambassador</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Nov 2024 15:52:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
